The paper discusses a machine learning scenario (federated learning) and proposes solutions to improve its robustness and hyper-parameter tuning. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed solutions involve matching feature representations (cs.CV) and using an online version of the REINFORCE algorithm (cs.DC, cs.SY) for hyper-parameter tuning.
